{"tid":2208277,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「岳男」獄中來信感激寫信師 月底推《自由山岳》攝影集約定登頂見","createTime":"2020-09-18T18:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T03:23:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"380ea7573af8e7e390b399328c4319b75bc761e7","tid":2208277,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WHIR-ZERO-112082666891998/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWHIR-ZERO-112082666891998%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=febf0605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WHIR-ZERO-112082666891998/</a><br />\n<br />\n被網民稱為「岳義士」的少年陳以晉，因去年9月時為救其他示威者而用棍打警察，於3個月前被判入獄10個月，目前在壁屋服刑。他所設立的Facebook專頁「WHIR ZERO」日前貼出他在獄中寄出的信，感謝有同道在《蘋果》登廣告祝他生日快樂，又代其他在囚抗爭者感激一班「寫信師」，指每次收到外面寄來的信件都感到窩心，鼓勵港人「只有堅定的靈魂，才能夠堅持做自己」。<br />\n<br />\n專頁亦表示他將會出攝影集，內容環繞着香港和外地的攀山涉水與運動，預計9月底就可出貨。<br />\n<br />\n署名「岳」的陳以晉，在獄中來信中代表其他在囚手足，感謝一眾同路人沒有忘記他們，指「寫信師」的心意他們都收到，又引述《解悶工廠》歌詞「如漫漫長夜手中信能助你一把」，感激大家忙碌中仍抽時間動筆寫信。<br />\n<br />\n「岳義士」在信中亦呼籲同路人去做「旁聽師」，支持即將要上庭的抗爭者，指當中很多都是為香港付出了青春去換取自由的年輕人，呼籲大家幫忙聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/HYJJXHSQQRAPVFMIAY23ZQRL2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FHYJJXHSQQRAPVFMIAY23ZQRL2I%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=1ba96ec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FHYJJXHSQQRAPVFMIAY23ZQRL2I%2F&h=77542dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/HYJJXHSQQRAPVFMIAY23ZQRL2I/</a>"},{"pid":"50c66228aa7ce978c2e6282f204f23152b5af73f","tid":2208277,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"其實今次亦不是第一次有抗爭者出版攝影集。在2016年旺角暴動案中罪成、被判囚7年的盧建民（影攝食），早前亦出版《影攝食－ 盧建民攝影集》，並將部份收入捐予「星火同盟」、「612 人道支援基金」等。該本攝影集頗受歡迎，在網上已告售罄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/moviesfeeding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmoviesfeeding%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=ac4f8d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/moviesfeeding/</a>"},{"pid":"593c5a4807bd42ecd7688a246c57b770a688f58b","tid":2208277,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db172698a9b63adab3f350cbbc8bcb19315984","tid":2208277,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b11ef4a73f463ccb4539f890a6bf882c82edf57","tid":2208277,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d7700f25178b998af5073bf394fe6095ab03a8","tid":2208277,"uid":266621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"支持岳巴"},{"pid":"5168af7cc0a2006cf50d1b3235d7fa4a2f70d677","tid":2208277,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"593c5a4807bd42ecd7688a246c57b770a688f58b","tid":2208277,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"